                    },
                    "body": "Though I don't have time right now to distill into a minimal reprex (in fact it is sort of the opposite; sorry!), the `targets` pipeline in this [repo|https://github.com/bcgov/climate-disturbances] reliably (at least on my machine) experiences an issue with multithreading on Windows to extent that I did have to add [this|https://github.com/bcgov/climate-disturbances/blob/72533ac2fc9cef8a154e898a09691689030acced/_targets.R#L35] in to stop it from simply hanging on Windows. I'm not sure how helpful this is but up to this point I have to reliably reproduce this issue.",
